Mr. Isa Rambo, the Area Commander, Suleja Area Command of the Nigeria Police Force, has been kidnapped by gunmen around Kaduna. A senior police officer told Sunday Punch that Rambo, who is an Assistant Commissioner of Police, was kidnapped on his way to Jos on Saturday evening. “He was kidnapped around Kaduna and was on his way to Jos along with his driver when they were attacked and whisked away. The kidnappers have made contact with us and are demanding a ransom of N50m,” he said. When Punch contacted, the Force Public Relations Officer, Frank Mba, said he was not aware.